{{CatTrack}}{{backlog|100}}
{{Wikipedia category|hidden=yes}}
This category contains all pages labeled with inline [[WP:WEASEL|weasel word]]-related templates such as {{tl|WW}}, {{tl|Weasel-inline}}, {{tl|Who}}, or {{tl|Which}}. It exists primarily for bot-based monitoring of articles containing weasel words. By-month categories are located in [[:Category:Articles with specifically marked weasel-worded phrases]].
The key to improving weasel words in articles is to either: a) name a source for the opinion; or b) change any opinionated language to concrete facts. After making such changes, remove the template from the article.
{{center|[[Special:RandomInCategory/All articles with specifically marked weasel-worded phrases|{{Clickable button|Fix one!|color=blue}}]]}}
